<H3>Landmark Cases Relating to the Telecomm Bill's &quot;Indecency&quot;
Provisions.</H3>
<P></P>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<P><B>1977 -- Federal Communications Commission  v.  Pacifica Foundation</B><BR>

<A HREF="http://www.aclu.org/court/fcc.html">Summary of Argument in ACLU amicus
brief</A><BR> 
<A HREF="http://www.aclu.org/court/pacifica.html">Syllabus of US Supreme Court
Decision  
</A><BR><A HREF="http://www.at.nwu.edu/cases/77-528/"><IMG
SRC="/graphics/ra.gif" BORDER="0">Listen to the Oral Arguments</A></P>
<P><B>1970 -- Paul Robert Cohen     v.     California</B><BR> 
<A HREF="http://www.aclu.org/court/cohen.html">Summary of Argument in ACLU
