<P> 
<B><A NAME="pinet">Capital Square Review</A>                         and 
Advisory Board et al                                            v.              
                     Pinette et al. 
</B> 
</P>
<P></P>
<DL>
<DD> Decided June 29, 1995.  The Ku Klux Klan submitted a form to the Capital 
Square Review in Ohio, requesting permission to display an unattended cross
during the Christmas season.  This suit was filed by the Klan after the   review
board denied the request. 
