<DT></DT></DL><IMG SRC="/graphics/redline.gif">
<P> 
<B><A NAME="jenkins">State of Missouri, et al.   v.  Kalima Jenkins, et al.,</A>

</B> 
</P>
<P></P>
<DL>
<DD>  Decided June 12, 1995. Missouri is challenging the District Court's
ruling that requires the State &quot;(1) to fund salary increases for virtually
all instructional and noninstructional staff within the Kansas City, Missouri,
School District  (KCMSD), and (2) to continue to fund remedial 'quality
education' programs because student  achievement levels were still 'at or below
national norms at many grade levels'.&quot;     
