            Nashville Banner Publishing Co.</A> 
</B> 
</P>
<P></P>
<DL>
<DD> Decided January 23, 1995.  &quot;Alleging that her discharge by respondent
Nashville Banner Publishing Company violated the Age Discrimination in
Employment Act of 1967 (ADEA), petitioner McKennon filed suit seeking a  variety
of legal and equitable remedies available under the ADEA, including backpay.&quot;
  
