<TD ROWSPAN="1"><FONT SIZE="+1">Wednesday, <BR>March 19</FONT></TD>
<TD>
<P ALIGN="CENTER"><B>96-511<BR> RENO v. ACLU</B></P></TD>
<TD>Is the Communications Decency Act, which makes it a crime to display &quot;indecent&quot;
materials over the internet if they are available to minors, unconstitutional? 
The ACLU's brief in the case is due February 20th.</TD></TR></TABLE>
