<H2>1995 Court Term</H2>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="/court/summmem.html">Review</A></LI>
<LI><A HREF="/news/n062896a.html">June 28, 1996 News Release</A></LI></UL>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<H3>Preview by Issue</H3>
<P><A HREF="http://www.aclu.org/court/intro95.html"><B>Introduction and ACLU
Participation before the Court</B>, ACLU Legal Director Steven R. Shapiro</A><BR>

<A HREF="http://www.aclu.org/court/habeas95.html"><B>Criminal Justice</B>,
ACLU General Counsel Vivian Berger</A><BR> 
<A HREF="http://www.aclu.org/court/lgrght95.html"><B>Lesbian and Gay Rights</B>,
ACLU Lesbian and Gay Rights Project Director Matt Coles</A><BR> 
<A HREF="http://www.aclu.org/court/race95.html"><B>Racial Equality</B>, ACLU
General Counsel James Ferguson</A><BR> 
<A HREF="http://www.aclu.org/court/legal95.html"><B>&quot;Judicial Restraint&quot;</B>,
ACLU General Counsel Frank Askin</A></P></BLOCKQUOTE>
