http://www.aclu.org:80/library/pbp11.html 204.243.96.55 19970213120121 text/html 30515
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 13-Feb-97 12:00:09 GMT
Last-modified: Saturday, 27-Jan-96 17:52:24 GMT
