http://www.aclu.org:80/library/pbp18.html 204.243.96.55 19970213125603 text/html 16174
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 13-Feb-97 12:54:50 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 10-Oct-96 21:21:49 GMT
Content-length: 15986
