http://www.aclu.org:80/congress/cybrltr.html 204.243.96.55 19970213142216 text/html 11395
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 13-Feb-97 14:20:58 GMT
Last-modified: Saturday, 27-Jan-96 17:52:04 GMT
Content-length: 11207
