<H3 ALIGN="CENTER"><A HREF="/issues/cyber/trial/appeal.html">ACLU v. Reno</A></H3>
<P ALIGN="CENTER">Trial information and updates</P>
<H3 ALIGN="CENTER"><A HREF="http://www.aclu.org/library/ctstrip.html">Court
Stripping: Congress Undermines the Power of the Judiciary</A></H3>
<P ALIGN="CENTER"><FONT SIZE="-1">The American Civil Liberties Union released
a special report that examines how a series of legislative actions this Spring
are undermining fundamental constitutional rights by eroding the independence, 
scope and power of the Federal court system.  
</FONT></P>
